SUMMARY:Librarian: Tidy Up the Arcane Library! | Please Return All
 Grimoires to Their Correct Dimension
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new magical adventure begins! Tonight we're taking on
 the impossible task of organising an arcane library where the books have a
 habit of escaping reality. What could possibly go wrong? Librarian: Tidy
 Up the Arcane Library! is a single-player simulation. You need return
 scattered books to proper places in an Arcane Library. As completed rows
 of bookshelves, you can learn ability to improve your efficiency. Use your
 skills and strategies to shelve 3,072 books as quick as you can.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TiFRF9yfh0w
CATEGORIES:Librarian: Tidy Up the Arcane Library!
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23942211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260627T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260722T232600Z
DTSTART:20260718T203000Z
DTEND:20260718T223000Z
SUMMARY:Fallout 4 | Ep. 54 - Far Harbor Seems Lovely This Time of Year
DESCRIPTION:Our adventure through Far Harbor continues. The scenery is
 beautiful... the locals are mysterious... and the fog definitely isn't
 hiding anything dangerous. As the sole survivor of Vault 111, you enter a
 world destroyed by nuclear war. Every second is a fight for survival, and
 every choice is yours. Only you can rebuild and determine the fate of the
 Wasteland. Welcome home.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qAmtgSOWKuI
CATEGORIES:Fallout 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
