SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 40 - Today's Forecast: 100% Chance of
 Concrete
DESCRIPTION:Construction continues with another evening of heavy
 machinery, ambitious projects, and enough concrete to pave several
 lifetimes. Construction Simulator is back - bigger and better than ever!
 Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them brand new to the
 franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge maps - on your
 own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJ7t7eLr6eA
CATEGORIES:Construction Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23972211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260630T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260722T232600Z
DTSTART:20260721T203000Z
DTEND:20260721T223000Z
SUMMARY:DrainSim | Ep. 2 - She's Chock-a-Block, This One
DESCRIPTION:Back into the wonderfully satisfying world of drainage
 maintenance. Time to solve another blocked drain and probably become far
 too invested in pipe inspections. Dive into DrainSim and seize control of
 the floods! Clear the city's submerged streets, with a huge range of
 different tools from rakes to submersible pumps. Embrace the satisfaction
 of restoring the water flow. Become the city's hero, one drain at a time.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_T_3qvHHdUM
CATEGORIES:DrainSim
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
