DTSTAMP:20260701T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260722T232600Z
DTSTART:20260722T203000Z
DTEND:20260722T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite III | Ep. 9 - Target Hitler: Hunt the Grey Wolf DLC
DESCRIPTION:One of the most iconic missions in the series awaits. Stealth,
 patience, and precision are the order of the day as we tackle this
 legendary DLC. Sniper Elite 3 is a tactical third-person shooter that
 combines stealth, gameplay choice and genre-defining ballistics with huge,
 open levels and the exotic terrain of World War 2 North Africa.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite III
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
