SUMMARY:WET | Ep. 1 - Cool People Don't Use Stairs
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new series begins! It's time for stylish action,
 outrageous stunts, and discovering whether running across walls is a valid
 health and safety strategy. A stylish action shooter that blends
 fast-paced gunplay, sword combat, and cinematic acrobatics. Players follow
 mercenary Rubi Malone as she takes on dangerous jobs, battling through
 waves of enemies using slow-motion stunts inspired by classic action
 films. Expect explosive set pieces, over-the-top action, and plenty of
 style.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:WET
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
