SUMMARY:Red Dead Redemption II | Ep. 16 - A Cold Campfire and a Warm
 Revolver
DESCRIPTION:The journey across the frontier continues, bringing more
 unforgettable storytelling, difficult choices, and quiet moments before
 the next storm. Arthur Morgan and the Van der Linde Gang are outlaws on
 the run. With federal agents and bounty hunters massing on their heels,
 the gang must rob, steal, and fight their way across the rugged heartland
 in order to survive.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Red Dead Redemption II
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
